manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: ArmorSuit Designed for Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra Screen Protector 2 Pack Case Friendly MilitaryShield - Made in the USA

ArmorSuit MilitaryShield features exceptional clarity and UV protection to prevent yellowing. It is made from the same protective film material used to protect military aircraft, helicopters, and space shuttles. MilitaryShield is also equipped with "self-repairing" properties to maximize protection. The self-healing technology works to constantly eliminate minor scratches on the film. All of our MilitaryShield are uniquely designed to provide a perfect cut for a perfect fit on your device. It also features corrosion and moisture protection to prevent substances from migrating through the film to attack underlying substrates. It's designed to provide daily protection against scratches and reduce the chances of damage to your screen from impact forces and drops. Best of all, it's very easy to apply. Lifetime Replacement Promise If your MilitaryShield peels off, becomes scratched or damaged, or has installation flaws, we will gladly replace the product FREE OF CHARGE no matter what the issue is. If you ever need to remove the MilitaryShield, simply peel it off slowly with your bare hands. It will come off clean without any sticky residue. *Made in the USA* What's in the box 2x MilitaryShield Screen Protector Films1x Installation Spray1x Squeegee1x Microfiber ClothInstallation Video LinkLive-Chat Support QR Code

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Bubble free easy install...
reviews.reviewText: Just bought a S24 Ultra and put one of these Screen Protectors on right away. I've used AmorSuit protectors for years. They go on wet so you can move them around a bit before the final positioning. They are bubble free. Even if you have minor bubbles they will heal over the matter of a few days. The tough screen is not interfered with and the finger print sensor works perfectly. I highly recommend this protector for your phone screen. Absolutely the best.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Amazing S24 Ultra Screen Protector with One Flaw
reviews.reviewText: Overall impressed with the quality of the protector. I've used spigen, amfilm, and others in the past, so I've got something to compare to. I usually go with tempered glass, but chose not to due to the 24 Ultra having antiglare glass.The good:Application was simple and effective. Followed instructions and had zero issues and zero bubbles. After applying, I set a timer for 30 minutes and let it sit.The protector is crystal clear and doesn't interfere with touch functions at all. I didn't even have to re-register my fingerprints.The bad:My only gripe is that the protector does not cover the whole screen. There's a pretty noticeable gap all around the screen that is unprotected. If you're not looking for tempered glass, this would be a perfect 5/5 if not for the gaps.

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Long term review
reviews.reviewText: Purchased in Oct 2020Initial application was easy enough, no bubbles, case friendlywithin a few months, around the edges plastic was getting raised and small amounts of pocket lint was getting under, but not a big deal, when applied on the screen its hard to notice, it was usable and protectiveBut over time it also becomes brittle, so the corner separated while I was pulling the phone out of pocket and then I noticed how much the color changed, it is placed on top of a glass screen protector for comparison in this photo
The protection screen leaves an off color making it extremely noticeable. I took it off right away.
